---
// src/pages/index.astro
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <title>Global Veteran Electronics Hub</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-100 font-mono min-h-screen">
  
  <nav class="border-b border-zinc-800 p-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
    <div class="text-xl font-bold tracking-wider text-amber-500">VETERAN.CORE //</div>
    <div class="space-x-6 text-sm">
      <a href="/zh" class="text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100">中文</a>
      <a href="/bom-hub" class="bg-amber-500 text-zinc-950 px-4 py-1.5 font-bold hover:bg-amber-400 transition">BOM HUB</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-24 pb-16 px-6 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 uppercase tracking-tight leading-none">
      Don't just buy components. <br/>
      <span class="text-amber-500">Source with 20 years of hardware expertise.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      [LOCATION: SHENZHEN] // Independent analysis, QC standards, and strategic component optimization for global engineers.
    </p>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    
    <div class="bg-zinc-900 p-8 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-amber-500/50 transition duration-300">
      <div class="text-amber-500 text-xs font-bold mb-4">// MODULE_01</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 uppercase">China vs Global</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Deep-dive reliability testing, cross-reference analysis, and the truth about domestic equivalents vs Tier-1 brands.
      </p>
      <span class="text-amber-500 text-sm font-bold">ACCESS_LOGS -></span>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-zinc-900 p-8 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-amber-500/50 transition duration-300">
      <div class="text-amber-500 text-xs font-bold mb-4">// MODULE_02</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 uppercase">BOM Optimization</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Cost-down strategies without quality compromise. Lifecycle management and supply chain risk mitigation guidelines.
      </p>
      <span class="text-amber-500 text-sm font-bold">ACCESS_LOGS -></span>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-zinc-900 p-8 border border-zinc-800 hover:border-amber-500/50 transition duration-300">
      <div class="text-amber-500 text-xs font-bold mb-4">// MODULE_03</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 uppercase">About Me</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Based in Shenzhen since 2006. 20-year veteran electronics sourcing expert. Your transparent eyes and ears in the market.
      </p>
      <span class="text-amber-500 text-sm font-bold">ACCESS_LOGS -></span>
    </div>

  </main>

</body>
</html>
